headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Sky-High Profits for Los Santos Smugglers on Air Freight Cargo
content:
The black market for air-freighted contraband around Los Santos is booming, and with this surging demand for airborne cargo, profits for smugglers are sky high this week.

If your Hangar is jam-packed with valuables, offloading them in Air Freight Cargo Sell Missions will result in a bonus of 50% more GTA$ and RP.
